A recruiter or hiring manager gets multiple strong signals from such a project:

- **End-to-end product thinking**: Clear user, clear pain point (translating intent into architecture), and an opinionated workflow.
- **System design ability**: Sophisticated pipeline, job orchestration, and smart state modeling—much closer to real-world problems than toy apps.
